Style "FvwmPager-Desker" NoTitle, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, \
	NoHandles NoLenience, BorderWidth 0, TitleAtBottom
AddToMenu MenuFvwmWindowMove "" Nop
+ "Desk 	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	MoveToDesk 0 0
+ "Web/Mail	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	MoveToDesk 0 1
+ "Devel	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	MoveToDesk 0 2
+ "Games	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	MoveToDesk 0 3

AddToMenu MenuFvwmWindowGroupOps "" Nop
+ "Desk		Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	Pick All ($r) MoveToDesk 0 0
+ "Web/Mail	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	Pick All ($r) MoveToDesk 0 1
+ "Devel	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	Pick All ($r) MoveToDesk 0 2
+ "Games	Desk%menu/window-move.xpm%"	Pick All ($r) MoveToDesk 0 3

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPager-Desker: *
*FvwmPager-Desker: Geometry 255x55+5000+5000
*FvwmPager-Desker: Rows 1

*FvwmPager-Desker: Colorset * 14
*FvwmPager-Desker: HilightColorset * 15
*FvwmPager-Desker: BalloonColorset * 16
*FvwmPager-Desker: WindowColorsets 1 2

*FvwmPager-Desker: Font -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmPager-Desker: LabelsBelow
*FvwmPager-Desker: SolidSeparator
*FvwmPager-Desker: SmallFont 5x8
*FvwmPager-Desker: Balloons            All
*FvwmPager-Desker: BalloonFont         -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmPager-Desker: BalloonYOffset      +2
*FvwmPager-Desker: BalloonBorderWidth  1

*FvwmPager-Desker: Label 0 Main
*FvwmPager-Desker: Label 1 Web/Mail
*FvwmPager-Desker: Label 2 Devel
*FvwmPager-Desker: Label 3 Games
